00:15:02.110 --> 00:15:05.590
People who are in the hospital
and are there for a long stay

00:15:05.590 --> 00:15:07.550
and have some kind of extensive
surgery, morphine

00:15:07.550 --> 00:15:08.550
dosage goes up and up.

00:15:08.550 --> 00:15:10.240
Because our tolerance
goes up an up.

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:12.490
But tolerance is related
to acclimation

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:13.710
is related to immunity.

00:15:13.710 --> 00:15:16.350
And all of us have experienced
