00:31:05.990 --> 00:31:08.611
BOB SULLIVAN: We'll discuss
that later.

00:31:08.611 --> 00:31:10.410
HUGH THOMPSON: It
was researched.

00:31:10.410 --> 00:31:12.930
The Colombia students told me.

00:31:12.930 --> 00:31:15.320
BOB SULLIVAN: So another one
of the things that really

00:31:15.320 --> 00:31:17.350
makes small businesses plateau,
we have a lot of

00:31:17.350 --> 00:31:19.860
