00:32:32.470 --> 00:32:36.120
So pretotyping is create
a pre prototype.

00:32:36.120 --> 00:32:37.130
Even if it doesn't work.

00:32:37.130 --> 00:32:40.590
Even if there's humans in the
back end filling out forms and

00:32:40.590 --> 00:32:42.200
giving you responses.

00:32:42.200 --> 00:32:46.010
The idea behind a pretotype is
you'll quickly know if there's

00:32:46.010 --> 00:32:49.590
a response to it by the
user community.

00:32:49.590 --> 00:32:53.830
Pretotyping is becoming a very,
very powerful way for

00:32:53.830 --> 00:32:56.300
